60
00:05:53,624 --> 00:05:56,745
[SPEAKER_24]: The Chevalier Theatre is now a first-class performing arts center

61
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,751
[SPEAKER_24]: for the community to enjoy.

62
00:06:01,113 --> 00:06:09,459
